title: The Rangeland Avenger
creator: Max Brand
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Rangeland Avenger, by Max Brand. Read by Richard Kilmer. If you enjoy a fast moving western dealing with vengeance and well-deserved payback, you'll like The Rangeland Avenger by Max Brand. A soft spoken but ruthless gunman cuts a path of deadly payback across the Wild West in this exciting adventure. (Summary by Richard Kilmer) For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
